flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> LoadInterfaces[Load interfaces and routing table]
    
    LoadInterfaces --> ForEachIPv6{For each IPv6 address}
    
    ForEachIPv6 --> IsLinkLocal{Is it a link-local address?}
    
    IsLinkLocal -- Yes --> SendNSLinkLocal[Send Neighbor Solicitation to Solicited-Node multicast address\nff02::1:ffXX:XXXX\nMAC dst: 33:33:ff:XX:XX:XX]
    SendNSLinkLocal --> WaitNA[Wait for Neighbor Advertisement]
    WaitNA --> MarkActive[Mark host as active]
    
    IsLinkLocal -- No --> IsOnLink{Is the address in an on-link prefix?}
    
    IsOnLink -- Yes --> SendNSOnLink[Send Neighbor Solicitation to Solicited-Node multicast address\nff02::1:ffXX:XXXX\nMAC dst: 33:33:ff:XX:XX:XX]
    SendNSOnLink --> WaitNA
    
    IsOnLink -- No --> Remote[Remote address]
    Remote --> SelectInterface[Select interface and router]
    SelectInterface --> SendEchoRequest[Send ICMPv6 Echo Request via router\nMAC dst: router's MAC]
    SendEchoRequest --> WaitEcho[Wait for Echo Reply]
    WaitEcho --> MarkActive
    
    MarkActive --> NextIP[Proceed to next IPv6 address]
    NextIP --> ForEachIPv6
    
    ForEachIPv6 -- all addresses processed --> End([End])
